Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.79,0:00:29.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:29.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.26,0:00:34.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:34.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.88,0:00:44.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:44.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:49.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1179.518,406)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:54.70,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(404,396)}蟹堡恐惧症
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.04\pos(336,424)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:58.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.04\pos(479.502,746)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:58.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(400.547,445.334)\frz30.63}技术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:58.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.63\pos(530.728,699.334)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:02.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz31.17\pos(421.346,528.667)}制片指导
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:02.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:04.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(586,336)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.52,0:01:09.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算画完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.52,0:01:09.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finished at last
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.21,0:01:11.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们说我的大作怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:11.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you boys think of me masterpiece?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:15.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(304,1022)}新营业时间\N早上七点到晚上十一点
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.97,0:01:16.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:16.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.60,0:01:18.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:18.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is totally unfair
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.83,0:01:21.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥说得对  太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:21.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's right, that's totally unfair
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.14,0:01:23.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不能选个早于六点的上班时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:23.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Couldn't we get to work earlier than 6:00 a.m.?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.57,0:01:25.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就比如早上五点半
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.57,0:01:25.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like 5:30 a.m.?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.26,0:01:26.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者早上五点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.26,0:01:26.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or 5:00 a.m.?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.44,0:01:27.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者早上四点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:27.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or 4:00 a.m.?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.29,0:01:28.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:28.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Zip it
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.30,0:01:30.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:30.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:34.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(322,778)}海之霸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:34.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(846,242)}现在\N{\fnArial}23{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}小时营业
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.32,0:01:33.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海之霸要23小时营业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:33.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Chum Bucket open 23 hours
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.12,0:01:37.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说那个小废物痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:37.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, that little piece of flotsam Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.07,0:01:39.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以为自己营业时间能比我长是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:39.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thinks he can stay open longer than me, does he?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.77,0:01:40.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.77,0:01:40.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.40,0:01:41.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.40,0:01:41.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.10,0:01:41.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:41.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那他就错了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, he's wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.00,0:01:43.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:43.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, sure
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.83,0:01:48.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在起   蟹堡王24小时营业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:48.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As of now, the Krusty Krab is open 24 hours
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.02,0:01:50.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见没  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:50.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.85,0:01:53.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要一直工作工作工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:53.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We get to keep working and working and working
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.90,0:01:56.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也用不着回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:56.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without ever having to go home
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.37,0:01:59.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,掐自己一下  我一定是在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:59.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to pinch myself 'cause I must be dreaming
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.42,0:02:11.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:11.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:16.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\pos(648,776)}24{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}小时营业
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.85,0:02:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,24小时营业是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open 24 hours, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.25,0:02:20.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他果然会忍不住想要比我营业久一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:20.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew he couldn't resist staying open later than me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:23.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(696,530)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.62,0:02:23.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的邪恶大计进行得太顺利了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:23.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My evil plan is working perfectly
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.24,0:02:26.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会把他的员工累垮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:26.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll run his employees into the ground
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.32,0:02:30.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等到海绵宝宝累到神志不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:27.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and when SpongeBob's mind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:30.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,finally cracks from exhaustion
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.16,0:02:34.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就能让他告诉我蟹黄堡秘方了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:34.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get him to tell me the secret Krabby Patty formula
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.27,0:02:41.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么不笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:41.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you laughing?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.47,0:02:43.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这笑话我早听过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've heard this joke before
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(324,416)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.35,0:02:49.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王现在已经第三天不间断服务了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:46.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab is entering
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,day three of nonstop service
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.91,0:02:52.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鼓掌欢庆第三天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:52.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's give it up for day three
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.37,0:02:54.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第三天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:54.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Day three
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.77,0:02:57.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡  我不在乎是不是非得营业
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:57.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty, I don't care if we have to stay open
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.52,0:02:59.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到世界末日之后的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:59.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,till the day after the end of time
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.95,0:03:03.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但只要有你  我就圆满了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:03.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm with you, I'm complete
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第十天不间断服务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Day ten of nonstop service
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.25,0:03:09.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我能回家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:09.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, can I go home yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.84,0:03:11.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁都不准回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:11.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one goes home
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.12,0:03:12.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看看我的眼袋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:12.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at these bags under my eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.85,0:03:14.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连眼袋都有眼袋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:14.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even my bags have bags
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别瞎抱怨了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quit your bellyaching, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.78,0:03:20.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你听过海绵宝宝在那瞎抱怨没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:20.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't hear SpongeBob complaining, do you?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.34,0:03:25.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说蟹黄堡儿就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:25.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,K-R-A-B-B-Y P-A-T-T-Y, says I
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你倒是能向那小子学点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can learn a few things from that boy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.65,0:03:30.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  他不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:30.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, he is not normal
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.55,0:03:34.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  你可以坐下休息五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:34.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, you can sit down for five minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.45,0:03:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后继续工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then it's back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.65,0:03:39.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:39.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drat
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.50,0:03:42.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是没累垮他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:42.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not collapsing from exhaustion
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.34,0:03:44.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但只要再加点压力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:44.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But with a little more pressure
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.38,0:03:46.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝马上就会崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:46.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Sponge will crack like an egg
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.92,0:03:51.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后我就能尽情利用他破碎的心智了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:49.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be there to feast on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the goo of his shattered psyche
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.28,0:03:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜘蛛虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A spider bug
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:59.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(576,698)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, come on
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.22,0:04:01.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:01.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不打烊的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The restaurant that never closes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.41,0:04:04.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要点餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:04.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'd like to place an order?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.88,0:04:06.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一万份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:06.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,10,000 Krabby Patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.81,0:04:10.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就去做  这位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:10.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll start your order right away, Mr., uh, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.05,0:04:11.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:11.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that name again?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,彼老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peter Lankton
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.85,0:04:15.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:15.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.20,0:04:17.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这该不会是恶作剧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:17.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't some kind of prank, is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.52,0:04:19.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:19.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.57,0:04:19.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:19.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.97,0:04:21.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做好了就给你回电话  彼老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:21.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll call you when it's ready, Mr. Lankton
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全力冲刺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kick it into high gear
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大单子来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got a big order
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.46,0:04:26.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就指望你了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:26.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.60,0:04:28.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你举起锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:28.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need you to raise that spatular
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.34,0:04:32.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后我要你说  蟹堡王队加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:32.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I need you to say "Team Krusty Krab"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王队加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Team Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.75,0:04:35.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才像话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:35.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's me boy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.82,0:04:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我做一万份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, make me 10,000 patties
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.72,0:04:40.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准休息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:40.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And no breaks
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你听到没  锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that, spatula?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你  我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有一万份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and 10,000 Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.33,0:04:48.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且最棒的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:48.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the best part?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.81,0:04:50.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准休息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:50.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No breaks
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.27,0:04:53.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第15天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:53.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Day 15
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.97,0:04:56.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鼓掌欢庆第15天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:56.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it up for day 15
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.10,0:04:59.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说蟹黄堡儿就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:59.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,K-R-A-B-B-Y P-A-T-T-Y
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一千三百二十
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One thousand, three hundred, twenty
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第23天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Day 23
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鼓掌欢庆第23天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it up for day 23
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,6654
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,6,654
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.77,0:05:10.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第30天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:10.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Day 30
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,7121
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,7,121
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.02,0:05:17.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,8659
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:17.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,8,659
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, what's going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Day
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.11,0:05:23.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁知道多少天了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:23.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anyone know how many days it's been?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.58,0:05:24.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:24.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost track
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四十三天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forty-three
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.47,0:05:34.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:34.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the flimflam?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在里面干什么  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in here, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是在浪费我家粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're wasting all me food
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.99,0:05:40.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:40.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.19,0:05:45.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:45.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.17,0:05:46.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么时候来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:46.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When did you get in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子  我很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, I'm worried that
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.33,0:05:50.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见没
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:50.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.57,0:05:53.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:53.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.31,0:05:54.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不可以再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:54.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you run that by me again?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.81,0:05:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我之前说我很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, I said, I'm worried that
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚就以为你这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought you said
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在容我用这句话反驳一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let me offer this as a rebuttal
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.59,0:06:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,退后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay back
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.45,0:06:05.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我警告你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:05.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm warning you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这有点是在犯傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, now you're just acting silly
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是要你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.42,0:06:11.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吃我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:11.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't eat me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.40,0:06:12.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我嚼不烂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:12.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm too chewy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.52,0:06:19.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,见鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:19.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy shrimp
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.43,0:06:20.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:20.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're everywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.87,0:06:24.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:24.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就说那衣服太丑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you that shirt was hideous
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to live
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.12,0:06:39.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:39.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to live
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.57,0:06:43.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:43.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what's going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.15,0:06:47.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到处都是吃人蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:47.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everywhere I look, I see killer Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.35,0:06:48.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:48.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, there
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.59,0:06:51.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去工作必能解决一切问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:49.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that getting back to work won't solve
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.63,0:06:53.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你的锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:53.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your spatular
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spatular
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是烤架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here's the grill
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.12,0:06:57.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烤架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:57.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grill
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些是新鲜蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here are some fresh Krabby
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.13,0:07:07.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果然还是有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:07.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There may be a problem after all
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.53,0:07:08.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:08.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.74,0:07:11.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意思是你脑袋有毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:11.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It means there's something wrong with your head
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得你应该去找专业人士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, I think maybe you should see a professional
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.92,0:07:14.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摔跤手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:14.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wrestler?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.55,0:07:15.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:15.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,精神病医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A psychiatrist
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是要上哪找精神病医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But where am I going to find a psychiatrist
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.71,0:07:21.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:21.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at this
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:26.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(368,254)}彼老板精神病医生\N专治蟹堡恐惧症
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉不太好吧  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh, I don't know about this, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去看医生会不会误工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't I have to miss work if I went to see
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该就是这了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this looks like the place
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:36.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(818,908)}彼老板精神病医生
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.95,0:07:39.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:39.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.17,0:07:40.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:40.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doctor?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.99,0:07:42.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进  海绵宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:42.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come in, Mr. SquarePants
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1098,148)}彼老板医生
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请在沙发上就座
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, have a seat on the couch
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.30,0:07:47.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:47.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.17,0:07:53.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来让你把有害的信息抛在脑后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:51.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's unload all that harmful information
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in your little yellow head
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你比我想象的还要小啊  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a bit smaller than I imagined, Doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.52,0:07:57.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你才叫精神病医生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:57.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I guess that's why they call you a shrink
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:57.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(856,920)}缩              小
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.85,0:08:00.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说我还有救吗  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:00.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think there's hope for me, Doctor?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.25,0:08:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hope?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.75,0:08:01.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:01.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hope?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.20,0:08:03.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等秘方到我手上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:03.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When I get my hands on that formula
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.21,0:08:05.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就彻底没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:05.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there won't be any hope for any of you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.70,0:08:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你马上就能治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll be cured in no time
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.63,0:08:11.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:11.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先从简单的训练开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's start with a simple exercise
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.80,0:08:14.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要开合跳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:14.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jumping jacks?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.64,0:08:17.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:17.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to close your eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.97,0:08:19.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭紧点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:19.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tighter
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.07,0:08:20.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭紧点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:20.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tighter
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too tight
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.31,0:08:24.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我说你看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:24.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, tell me what you see
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.52,0:08:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看到巨型蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see giant Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.07,0:08:28.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:28.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.82,0:08:30.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡的成分是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:30.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what are they made of?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.99,0:08:31.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,憎恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:31.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hatred
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.86,0:08:33.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我是说食材
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:33.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I mean ingredients
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.12,0:08:34.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到底有什么破食材
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:34.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are the stinking ingredients?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡来抓我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're coming for me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.81,0:08:38.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:38.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay back
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  你哪来的钢琴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, where'd you get that piano?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,试试别的疗法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're trying something else
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会说一个词  你要说出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to say a word, and I want you to say
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你最先想到的第一个词
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the first word that pops into your head
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.55,0:08:53.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:53.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Work
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.37,0:08:54.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:54.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Work
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.97,0:08:55.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:55.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.40,0:08:57.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:57.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bun
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.96,0:08:58.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:08:58.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bun
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.95,0:09:03.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说的词得跟我不一样才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:01.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, the key is to say something
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:03.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,different than what I say
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.36,0:09:05.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:05.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.69,0:09:06.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:06.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potato
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.19,0:09:06.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马铃薯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:06.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Po-tah-to
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.81,0:09:07.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,番茄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:07.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tomato
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,西红柿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To-mah-to
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.57,0:09:12.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我放了点卡片  卡片上面写了点词
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:12.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've laid out some words on cards here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.44,0:09:15.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是常见的厨房食材
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:15.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These words are common kitchen ingredients
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.02,0:09:18.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要什么顺序  就按那顺序排
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:18.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to arrange them in any order you choose
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.25,0:09:21.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能会排成诗歌  或者秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:21.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It could be a poem or a secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.92,0:09:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.15,0:09:24.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:24.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A secret formula, good
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.95,0:09:26.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就排这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:26.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's do that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.61,0:09:29.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害我有点紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:29.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're making me nervous
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.82,0:09:30.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:30.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.89,0:09:32.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就坐这了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:32.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be over here, then
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我排完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm finished
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我排成了钢琴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I arranged them into a piano
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.07,0:09:40.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,由于你的心智
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:40.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since your mind
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.10,0:09:43.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,目前为止都对各种精神疗法有抗性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:43.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has been resistant to every mental technique so far
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.44,0:09:44.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只好采取
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:44.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm forced to resort
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.83,0:09:48.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我手上最强大的疗法来治疗你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:48.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to my most powerful method of curing you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.07,0:09:48.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纤维吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:48.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fiber?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.77,0:09:49.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:49.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.78,0:09:50.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,催眠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:50.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hypnosis
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,催眠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hypnosis?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.05,0:09:54.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,眼睛盯着这只表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:54.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, keep your eyes on this watch
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.69,0:09:59.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我数到三  你就会沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:59.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When I count to three, you will fall into a deep sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.79,0:10:02.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:02.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然奏效了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it worked
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.04,0:10:12.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我打了响指
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:12.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, when I snap my fingers
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.32,0:10:16.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就会醒来  把秘方全告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:16.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you will awake and tell me the formula
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.21,0:10:21.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:21.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wake up
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有什么声音又吵又讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What else is loud and obnoxious?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.37,0:10:33.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么就是不醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:33.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why won't you wake up?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.25,0:10:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.21,0:10:58.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  听说你大脑不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:58.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, I heard your brain was sick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我给你带了这个披萨饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I brought you this cookie pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.45,0:11:02.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:02.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有巧克力奶给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here's some chocolate milk
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.67,0:11:06.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,风味乳饮料之王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:06.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The king of flavored dairy drinks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.36,0:11:10.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴我们又是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:10.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad we're friends again
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just remember, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都与你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll always be with you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,right here
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我心里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In my heart?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实是动脉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, in your arteries
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.12,0:11:20.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,麻烦快点醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:20.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, do me a favor and wake up
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wake up
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.42,0:11:25.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:25.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wake up
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.62,0:11:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It worked
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.37,0:11:30.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我康复了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:30.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm cured
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.46,0:11:31.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可秘方怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:31.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what about the formula?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.29,0:11:32.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:32.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I better get back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢帮忙  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything, Doc
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.82,0:11:36.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:36.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.66,0:11:38.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:38.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a lie
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.47,0:11:40.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,治疗没成功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:40.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Therapy doesn't really work
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.74,0:11:42.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还病着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:42.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're still sick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.31,0:11:44.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,病得可重了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.31,0:11:44.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very, very sick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.42,0:11:49.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴能看到你脑子恢复了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:49.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good to see your brain's all fixed, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  原来我睡一觉就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just needed some sleep is all
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.27,0:11:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能保证  再也不用24小时营业了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I can safely say, no more 24-hour shifts
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.87,0:11:57.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为23小时就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:57.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause 23 hours'll be plenty
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.30,0:11:59.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:11:59.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.85,0:12:05.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:05.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, seriously
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我继续工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back to work
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:10.04,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(397,394)}虚有其表
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(263.316,458)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(531.678,760)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:14.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:14.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(407.566,442)\frz29.52}技术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:14.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(529.736,692)\frz29.08}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:17.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.29\pos(421.602,536)}制片指导
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:17.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(442,466)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.33,0:12:22.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:22.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Easy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfection
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.05,0:12:29.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五号餐做好了没  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:29.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is number five's order ready yet, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.35,0:12:30.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再等一下  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:30.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a second, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.50,0:12:31.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:31.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's time for you to go now
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你长大得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You grew up so fast
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.10,0:12:36.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:36.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.77,0:12:39.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我答应过自己不会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:39.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promised myself I wouldn't do this
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.20,0:12:40.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你拿走吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:40.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just take it, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.65,0:12:41.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:41.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it away
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.75,0:12:45.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:45.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:48.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(428,312)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Number five
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.40,0:12:47.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:47.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Number five
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.64,0:12:48.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:48.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.03,0:12:52.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要赞美厨子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:52.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My compliments to the chef
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.70,0:13:00.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快出来  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:00.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come out here, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.82,0:13:04.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:04.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.11,0:13:06.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吵  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:06.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hush, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.00,0:13:08.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然会泄露我藏宝洞的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:08.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or you'll give away your location of me hidey hole
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.27,0:13:09.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,藏宝洞是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:09.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's a hidey hole?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.92,0:13:11.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我藏宝的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:11.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's where I hide me treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.76,0:13:14.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:14.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Catch
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.73,0:13:17.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快把宝箱搬去我办公室  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:17.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get that chest to me office, boy, pronto
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's in this thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.30,0:13:18.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝藏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:18.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Treasure?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算是财宝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A treasure trove of sorts
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.18,0:13:22.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我的回忆箱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:22.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me memory chest
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我海军服役时传下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from my years in the navy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.11,0:13:28.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛要挖海军回忆箱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:28.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why'd you dig up your navy chest, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.90,0:13:31.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟我的战友要开战友会了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:31.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, me navy buddies and I are having a reunion
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.12,0:13:33.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要穿回我的旧制服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:33.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanted to wear me old uniform
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.56,0:13:37.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有好多好酷的海军玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:37.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at all your cool navy stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.47,0:13:38.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:38.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arrgh
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.21,0:13:41.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我第一个纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:41.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me first tattoo
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Neat
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.24,0:13:45.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我的男子汉雄壮奖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:45.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this is me manly toughness trophy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么赢来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How'd you win that?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.20,0:13:47.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当上强人中的强人就赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:47.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By being the toughest of the tough
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那几位是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are those guys?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.47,0:13:51.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的船友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:51.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me shipmates
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最强大的航海帮派
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The toughest bunch to ever sail the briny deep
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有老铁眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's old Iron Eye
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,络腮胡  我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Mutton Chop, me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鱼雷肚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Torpedo Belly
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.27,0:14:02.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有锁齿琼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:02.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Lockjaw Jones
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有酷外号吗  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you have a cool nickname, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.03,0:14:05.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:05.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我曾经是铁甲金钟罩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was old Armor Abs Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,曾经是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.03,0:14:12.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你当年瘦多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:12.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you were thinner back then
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.67,0:14:13.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:13.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.18,0:14:16.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我的海军学员制服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:16.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is me navy cadet uniform
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.16,0:14:17.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好把话收回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:17.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prepare to eat your words
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我体重根本没增
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause I haven't put on more
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.92,0:14:20.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:20.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than a
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.85,0:14:21.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好几
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:21.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,couple of
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.82,0:14:22.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,磅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:22.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pounds
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.42,0:14:27.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  我是肥了点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:27.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, maybe I'm a bit bigger
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但还是强人中的强人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'm still the toughest of the tough
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.31,0:14:30.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来啊  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:30.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.24,0:14:31.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快打一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:31.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,give 'em a punch
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.32,0:14:33.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要我打你肚子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:33.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want me to punch you in the stomach?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.21,0:14:34.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是打肚子  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:34.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not in the stomach, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打铁甲金钟罩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in me armor abs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.83,0:14:42.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我整只手臂都碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:42.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My entire arm disintegrated
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝刀未老啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still got it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乖乖去打理工作环境吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be a good lad, go get your station in shipshape
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.82,0:14:49.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我这个老水手回味往日回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:49.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and leave an old sea dog to revel in his memories
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.09,0:14:50.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:50.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.28,0:14:52.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:52.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来把这里打理好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get this place shipshape
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们几个  别到处闹腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You men, stop playing around
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:57.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(970,626)}土豆
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前往战斗位置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To battle stations
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:58.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,178)}薯条
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全体成员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All hands on deck
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.18,0:15:04.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要有浓厚风味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:04.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That calls for full flavor
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.67,0:15:07.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,番茄酱芥末酱位于左舷前方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:07.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ketchup and mustard off the port bow
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.26,0:15:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡准备启航了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty ready to set sail
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.62,0:15:12.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:12.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.15,0:15:14.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:14.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.87,0:15:16.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:16.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.95,0:15:20.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:20.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.20,0:15:22.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:22.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.54,0:15:23.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:23.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You all right?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.16,0:15:25.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你困了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:25.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sleepy?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.06,0:15:30.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:30.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闻不出他脉搏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't smell his pulse
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.66,0:15:34.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么动静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:34.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.97,0:15:38.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁在那
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:38.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is somebody there?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别看我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.42,0:15:43.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离我远点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:43.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leave me be
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're alive
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.07,0:15:45.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:45.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.24,0:15:47.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没穿衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:47.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,naked
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's true
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我蜕皮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've molted
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.67,0:15:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么是蜕皮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's "molted"?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是螃蟹长太胖的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's when a crab gets too fat--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.44,0:15:54.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:54.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,well--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.78,0:15:56.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,套不进壳里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:56.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,outgrows his shell
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.32,0:15:57.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,壳会脱落
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:57.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It falls off
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.32,0:16:02.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铁甲金钟罩可不能这样到战友会露面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:02.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Armor Abs Krabs can't show up at the reunion like this
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.15,0:16:05.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全身粉嫩嫩软绵绵  算不上雄壮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:05.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All pink and soft and unmanly
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.82,0:16:09.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,浑身赘肉  没一点腹肌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:09.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm all flab and no ab
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.02,0:16:12.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:12.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.11,0:16:13.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:13.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.14,0:16:14.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉刚刚爆粗口了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:14.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about the foul language, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.95,0:16:18.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你表现完完全全就是虚有其表
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:15.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you're acting like
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:18.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there never was a man in that shell
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.07,0:16:20.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板参军那会儿可是无所畏惧的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:20.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krabs of his navy days was fearless
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.50,0:16:24.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝不会被丢壳这种小事拖累
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:22.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't let something as insignificant
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:24.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as a missing shell slow him down
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.84,0:16:25.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:25.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.88,0:16:29.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你样子又笨又粉又肉的又有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:29.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who cares how silly, pink and fleshy you look?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.07,0:16:32.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更何况你又手无缚鸡之力  又弱又废
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:32.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How non-threatening, limp, and soggy you are
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.93,0:16:33.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:33.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.51,0:16:37.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也没法出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:37.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't go anywhere ever again
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.50,0:16:38.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,傻子破烂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:38.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stupid, no good
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.75,0:16:49.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面好黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:49.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sure is dark in here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Mr. Krabs--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我变成你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.72,0:16:57.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你真是个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:57.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you're a genius
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.99,0:16:59.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴你懂我意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:59.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad you got my point
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.82,0:17:01.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外表不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:01.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not about what's on the outside
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.75,0:17:02.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内心才重要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:02.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's what's on the inside
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  你个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you barnacle brain
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.32,0:17:06.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的不是你的扯淡比喻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:06.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not your silly metaphor
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你  进我壳里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you, in me shell
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.82,0:17:09.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我想到办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:09.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It gives me an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.17,0:17:13.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以去战友会假装成我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:13.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can go to the reunion and pretend to be me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.01,0:17:15.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以当海军战友了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:15.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get to be a navy buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然你得先花点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course you'll need some time
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.60,0:17:18.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我性格学得像一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:18.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to approximate me personality
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.64,0:17:19.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:19.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll be a snap
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.65,0:17:20.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:20.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward and I
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.29,0:17:22.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有好多年都背着你偷偷学你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:22.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have been doing it behind your back for years
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.69,0:17:24.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  看看你学得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:24.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, show me what you got
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.56,0:17:27.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:27.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.37,0:17:28.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:28.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.55,0:17:29.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:29.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love money
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.52,0:17:31.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还算可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:31.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, that ain't half bad
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我曾经赢过一次马拉松
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I once won a marathon
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.17,0:17:35.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为终点线那边有人掉了一毛钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:35.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because someone dropped a penny at the finish line
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.45,0:17:39.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我每晚都给钱包盖被子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:39.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every night, I tuck me wallet in
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.50,0:17:41.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还给它讲睡前故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:41.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and tell it a bedtime story
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.40,0:17:43.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  小包包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:43.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, wallety
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.16,0:17:46.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好  我知道你学得很像了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:46.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay, I get the point
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.61,0:17:48.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:48.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.59,0:17:50.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我女儿珍珍要动手术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:50.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me daughter Pearl needs an operation?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.52,0:17:52.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我亲自去动  这样省钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:52.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll do it meself and save a nickel
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.27,0:17:58.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:58.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll do, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:01.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(346,446)}裤头村大会堂\N欢迎海军战友
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就试试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, here goes
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.35,0:18:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没见过这么多雄壮的海军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never seen so many manly naval men
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.32,0:18:09.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多强悍  多勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:09.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So tough, so brave
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.27,0:18:10.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:10.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(930,462)}欢迎海军战友
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.65,0:18:11.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:11.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,clever
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.72,0:18:13.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是他们的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:13.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm one of them
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.05,0:18:14.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:14.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you're not
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别给我搞砸了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't blow this for me, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.30,0:18:17.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会让你失望的  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:17.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't let you down, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.85,0:18:19.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铁甲金钟罩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:19.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Armor Abs Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.95,0:18:22.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跟战友一起来干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:22.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come join your old naval buddies in a toast
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.92,0:18:24.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:24.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.92,0:18:26.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我干了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:26.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.41,0:18:30.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就让派对号巨轮在这里抛锚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:30.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, boys, let the S.S. Party drop anchor right here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都怪我先前乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've created a monster
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.26,0:18:35.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来点烈酒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:35.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's some grog
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.92,0:18:38.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还是很喜欢菠萝  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:38.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You still like pineapple, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,何止喜欢菠萝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like pineapple?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.49,0:18:40.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家就是菠萝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:40.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I live in one
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.57,0:18:46.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹还是一样雄壮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:46.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That old Krabs is as manly as ever
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.15,0:18:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝居然成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob is pulling it off
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.55,0:18:51.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铁甲金钟罩  我老铁眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:51.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Armor Abs, old Iron Eye here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.35,0:18:54.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可恨不得想打下你的传奇大肚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:54.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has been itching to punch your legendary gut
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.80,0:18:56.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,觉得自己够雄壮就来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:56.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if you think you're man enough
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.35,0:18:58.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:58.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This could be bad
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.50,0:19:00.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发射鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:00.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire the torpedo
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.95,0:19:08.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:08.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.01,0:19:09.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟从前一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:09.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like old times
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.97,0:19:12.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一颗牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:12.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A tooth?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.04,0:19:13.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好几颗牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:13.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Teeth
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.73,0:19:15.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才叫雄壮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:15.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, that's manly
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.96,0:19:21.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:21.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He did it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  我的水兵们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, me swabbies
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.87,0:19:30.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在要来颁发男子汉雄壮奖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:30.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's time to award the trophy of manly toughness
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.18,0:19:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,获奖者久经岁月  依然气势磅礴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to a man whose toughness has stood the test of time
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.12,0:19:40.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就是铁甲金钟罩  尤金蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:40.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That man is Eugene Armor Abs Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.53,0:19:41.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上来吧  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:41.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come up here, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.91,0:19:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是我一生中最美好的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the best night of me life
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.07,0:19:47.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的战友依然觉得我很雄壮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:47.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me naval buddies still think I'm manly
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.13,0:19:47.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铁甲金钟罩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:47.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Armor Abs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.96,0:19:50.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还不必自惭形秽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:50.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I didn't have to shame myself
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.54,0:19:52.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢大家让我得奖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:52.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the trophy, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.45,0:19:56.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,致辞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:56.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Speech
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.55,0:19:57.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:57.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.20,0:19:57.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:57.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.71,0:19:59.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说几句话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:59.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say something
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.09,0:20:01.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来给大家讲个雄壮小故事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:01.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me spin you a manly yarn
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.76,0:20:02.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:02.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attaboy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.43,0:20:06.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我那时在水母田
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:06.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So there I was, in Jellyfish Fields
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.05,0:20:07.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:07.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm doomed
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.40,0:20:11.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡水已经少得可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:11.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me supply of bubble soap was dangerously low
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.40,0:20:13.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正当我吹出了最后一个泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:13.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And as I blew my last bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.78,0:20:16.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他刚刚说水母田吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:16.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did he say Jellyfish Fields?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.62,0:20:18.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吹泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:18.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blowing bubbles?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在水母田干什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What were you doing in Jellyfish Fields?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然是捉水母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, jellyfishing, of course
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.09,0:20:27.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有电话找蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:27.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Phone call for Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快下台
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off the stage
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.98,0:20:31.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:31.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I gotta go
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.37,0:20:31.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:31.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.50,0:20:36.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是想去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:36.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.57,0:20:37.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,众所周知
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:37.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody knows
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.88,0:20:41.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铁甲金钟罩有两件事绝对不会做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:41.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's two things old Armor Abs Krabs would never do
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.75,0:20:43.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:43.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.27,0:20:46.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一件就是花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:46.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Number one is spend a penny
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.37,0:20:48.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二件就是说走就走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:48.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the other one is leave
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.72,0:20:54.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没给鱼雷肚耍点你的招牌肚皮硬碰硬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:51.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without giving old Torpedo Belly
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:54.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one of your world-famous steely belly butts
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.22,0:20:59.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还以为你看穿我技俩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:20:59.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd seen through my ruse
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.05,0:21:01.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:01.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, arrgh
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.12,0:21:01.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们该不会以为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:01.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You didn't think
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.92,0:21:05.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只来领男子汉雄壮奖杯就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just gonna collect
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:05.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this here trophy of manly toughness
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.69,0:21:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可要另外提醒你们这些弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without reminding yous lily-livers
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打一开始为什么我得奖了  你们却没得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why you give it to me in the first place?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.41,0:21:11.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来硬碰硬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:11.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's have at it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.97,0:21:13.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别放水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:13.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No holding back
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.17,0:21:14.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,使出全力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:14.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it your all
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不敢看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't watch
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.60,0:21:23.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铁甲金钟罩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:23.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Armor Abs?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.20,0:21:35.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我我我我我我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:35.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I-I-I-I-I-I
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.07,0:21:38.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就先拿走我的男子汉雄壮奖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:38.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll just take my manly toughness trophy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.43,0:21:39.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.43,0:21:39.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and head home now
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.98,0:21:43.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,男子汉村再见  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:43.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you around Manville, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.41,0:21:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好汉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,men
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.40,0:21:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.03,0:21:49.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不是尤金蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:49.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not Eugene Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.32,0:21:51.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:51.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.66,0:21:54.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:54.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, lads
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.37,0:21:55.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:55.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a good look
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.25,0:21:58.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个才是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:58.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is who I am
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.20,0:22:01.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我蜕了壳  变得很
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:01.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've molted me shell and I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.24,0:22:03.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:03.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,vulnerable
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.21,0:22:06.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我绝不会吹泡泡又捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:06.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm certainly no bubble-blowing jellyfisher
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.22,0:22:07.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无意冒犯  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:07.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No offense, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.26,0:22:08.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没放心上  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:08.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,None taken, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.47,0:22:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.87,0:22:11.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.87,0:22:11.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go home
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.30,0:22:12.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:12.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.10,0:22:15.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有东西你忘带了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:15.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've forgotten something
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.73,0:22:18.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:18.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.27,0:22:20.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,承认你失去了自己的壳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.27,0:22:20.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Admitting you lost your shell
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.89,0:22:24.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我见过最强悍的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.89,0:22:24.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,was the toughest thing I've ever seen
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.97,0:22:26.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:26.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.50,0:22:27.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有话要坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.50,0:22:27.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a confession
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.37,0:22:30.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.37,0:22:30.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are fake
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.88,0:22:31.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.88,0:22:31.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.82,0:22:32.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.82,0:22:32.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.87,0:22:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也是吗  鱼雷肚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You too, Torpedo Belly?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.65,0:22:39.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实鱼雷很久以前就取出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.65,0:22:39.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, I had my torpedo removed long ago
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.34,0:22:43.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这牙已经不是我参军当年的牙了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:41.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And these aren't the same choppers
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:43.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I had in the navy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.47,0:22:47.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的铁眼其实是塑料装饰板做的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.47,0:22:47.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My iron eye is actually made of Formica
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.61,0:22:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看看  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.61,0:22:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at that, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.37,0:22:57.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你战友都有见不得人的小秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:22:57.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your navy buddies all had something to hide
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.10,0:22:59.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  太可悲了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:22:59.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, poor suckers
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.77,0:23:01.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码我壳还会再长回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:01.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least my shell will grow back
